public abstract class BaseTwoWayConverter<From,To> extends BaseConverter<From,To> implements TwoWayConverter<From,To>
Base class for implementing two-way converters.

Adds to BaseConverter an implementation of unconvert(Object) that checks for null, catches exceptions and called onUnconvert(Object).

Conversions

  • Converter.convert(Object) - Called to convert from => to
  • unconvert(Object) - Called to convert to => from

Implementing Converters

  • BaseConverter.onConvert(Object) - Called to convert from => to
  • onUnconvert(Object) - Called to convert to => from

Missing Values

  • nullValue()
